This document describe the files functions:

install-service.sh
   This script will deploy the edr-state-server service. This service will read the conf/state.conf and export via the HTTP protocol.

edr-state-server.service
   This is the service definition file.

state-server.py
   This is the main program of the service. It is a python script which run a simple http web server. It will return the data in conf/state.conf

state-monitor.py
